{"tid":22184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經][世界大戰] SLAM DUNK最強12人 歡迎討論","createTime":"2016-12-04T09:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T10:24:28.000Z","uid":43778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b83017bbc0fe164b3995f65502d6b568392245ec","tid":22184,"uid":43778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:47:45.000Z","msg":"大家討論下心目中最強陣容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正選<br />\nPG : 仙道 <br />\n最中意呢類高既keyman，同海南牧打個集真係丁死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSG : 神宗一朗<br />\n3分shooter，唔洗解釋啦<br />\n<br />\nSF : 流川楓<br />\n識得傳波既流川真係好神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />贏埋澤北呢個位本身仲有考慮土屋淳，不過佢係漫畫入面太少出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf09ee64aa4800ab690b9fb3031c7b743f8b951","tid":22184,"uid":43778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"PF : 河田雅史<br />\n全能型大前鋒，識key ball，識傳波，識射3分，識打底，防守搶板都勁，同Draymond Green差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nC : 森重寬<br />\n有速度(有集block完人即刻跑上去做alley opp，係中鋒黎講應該算快)，有力量，block shot勁。防守勁。進功都勁。傳統型既中鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fdfd451332763e633d5f3fe9587b1cea5a6f19","tid":22184,"uid":3443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:12:58.000Z","msg":"有無slam dunk poster 送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc8317263bee9d71b245374d7d4ae6e6c9e3b8b","tid":22184,"uid":43778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"後備<br />\nPG : 牧<br />\nkeyman黎講都唔洗點解釋<br />\n<br />\nSF : 澤北<br />\n雖然佢獨食，但係one on one無人mark到，好穩定既得分點<br />\n<br />\nSF : 土屋淳<br />\n漫畫好少見到佢，但單係睇佢打豐玉個場印象都幾深刻，同仙道個feel差唔多<br />\n<br />\nSG : 三井<br />\n純3分shooter，係故事入面好似無幾個，做定點射手一流<br />\n<br />\nSG : 諸星大<br />\n雙能衛，可以打keyman，又可以做搶分<br />\n<br />\nSG : 松本<br />\n如果澤北唔係山王既話，佢就係絕對王牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知真唔真，不過對湘北個陣見到佢識得自己keyball打，有創造力，都係穩定既得分點<br />\n<br />\nC : 櫻木<br />\n漫畫入面進攻好麻麻，但係防守，搶板，速度，力量，機動性都唔差，原型係Dennis Rodman，打小球必備球員"}]}